{"tid":2157101,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"希拉莉：若拜登勝選後邀請　不排除自己再任官職","createTime":"2020-08-14T21:32:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T04:36:23.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":64,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"d999093654dc714600883fce6dbd78a25d73eb0f","tid":2157101,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T21:32:15.000Z","msg":"美國前國務卿希拉莉表示，若民主黨總統參選人拜登入主白宮，她已經準備好以任何方式協助拜登政府，不排除可以在拜登政府出任官職。<br />\n<br />\n希拉莉出席一個論壇回應提問時說，現在是每一名美國國民，不論年齡、性別、種族，都應該挺身而出修補國家的時候，因此如果拜登當選而提出邀請，應該考慮幫忙，相信由拜登做總統可以團結國民。<br />\n<br />\n希拉莉又對拜登選擇賀錦麗為拍檔表示興奮，認為賀錦麗會是拜登的一位強勢拍檔。<br />\n<br />\n另外，在拜登宣布賀錦麗為競選拍檔之後，兩人在兩日內獲得4800萬美元的政治捐款，其中3900萬來自互聯網，金額超過拜登及賀錦麗兩人在去年全年獲得的政治捐款總數。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543840-20200815.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543840-20200815.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8WyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=f9a0208b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543840-20200815.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=df8e1c39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543840-20200815.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"7cb2630de43593caad8fd379eca8b1fb8f6cd261","tid":2157101,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T23:33:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"44c7caab3550cf6165dea2c4a89108f1ac026002","tid":2157101,"uid":127575,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T02:10:01.000Z","msg":"香港台灣即玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"718420995fa7e3fab93c05832ceb70b491c1d7c2","tid":2157101,"uid":21545,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T02:27:02.000Z","msg":"咁樣倒米"},{"pid":"fdbf5ed595f6ca05532dee96d9806591d612f7b5","tid":2157101,"uid":139613,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20